        },
        "content": "## Status meaning\n\n### Services\n- **Healthy**: Prometheus can scrape the service metrics endpoint\n- **Unhealthy**: scrape target is down\n\n### API endpoints\n- **Healthy**: requests seen in the last 15 minutes and no `5xx`\n- **Idle**: no requests in the last 15 minutes\n- **Unhealthy**: one or more `5xx` in the last 15 minutes\n\n`4xx` responses do **not** mark an endpoint unhealthy.",
